channel.title: Pi help with teleports
channel.description:
How would you change teleports in project insanity? Like I want to enable a bosses command for the falador teleport icon, and so on for the other 2 spellbooks, that will teleport someone to 5 different options they can choose like, King Black Dragon, Kalphite Queen, Chaos Elemental, Bork, and Barrelchest.
I know I have to do something with ClickingButtons.java and config.java, but what do I have to do? Please give me an example and explain thanks very much!
